Where does the oil come from? I did not take closeups (shame on me) but
you guys probably know how to interpret the oil leak, don't you? Is it
the shaft seal or the nose cone seal?

Also take a look at this:

http://picasaweb.google.de/timo.schairer/EngineDrop/photo#51819610264337
